creator: Dido Inc
descriptionHtml:
😍DIDO is a new free voice chat app!😍
In DIDO you will get laughs, happiness, surprises, new friends, you will relax... Make friends and find yours with who you can share the same interests. If you want to put more fun into your life, trust me, download this app because DIDO is a super voice chat party online!

FEATURES:

TOTALLY FREE — Enjoy free live voice chat over 3G, 4G, LTE or Wi-Fi.

PUBLIC CHAT ROOMS — Browse THOUSANDS live chat rooms from NEARBY or AROUND THE WORLD that cover thousands of topics.

PRIVATE CONVERSATIONS — Start private one-on-one text and voice conversations with your friends from anywhere in the world.

CHAT GAMES — Play games together directly in your chat group!

VIRTUAL GIFTS — Stunning animated gifts can be sent out to express your love.

SHARE and FOLLOW — Share your favorite ROOMS on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Snapchat and more, inviting friends and new followers.

Want more features? Get DIDO now!

Play games while chatting
You can play games like UNO while chatting in Room. Game is free on DIDO. You can play games with people all over the world anytime.

Free group voice chat
Create a group voice chat room, invite friends or wait for strangers to join in the chat room, use text or voice to chat with friends, enjoy the fun of a great voice chat party.

Voice chat tag
You can add topic tags to your voice chat rooms. There are different chat tags for chatting, entertainment, singing, and tons more. You can choose the chat room which you are interested in according to the topic. The tag will help you find friends with the same interests more accurately so that you guys will have more topics to talk about.

Awesome virtual gifts
DIDO offers lots of amazing virtual gifts, strengthen the friendship between you and your friends by sending cute virtual gifts. Everyone likes receiving gifts from others. Every gift from a friend is a wish for your happiness.

Easy to register
Use a message and Facebook to sign up for a DIDO account. It is easier and saves you more time. Enjoy your voice chat experience quickly and easily."

creator: SHFC Technology Limited
descriptionHtml:
DiDo is a voice chat app!
In DIDO you will get laughs, happiness, surprises, new friends, you will relax... Make friends and find yours with who you can share the same interests. If you want to put more fun into your life, trust me, download this app because DIDO is a super voice chat party online!

FEATURES:

TOTALLY — Enjoy live voice chat over 3G, 4G, LTE or Wi-Fi.

PUBLIC CHAT ROOMS — Browse THOUSANDS live chat rooms from NEARBY or AROUND THE WORLD that cover thousands of topics.

CHAT GAMES — Play games together directly in your voice chat!

VIRTUAL GIFTS — Stunning animated gifts can be sent out to express your mind.

SHARE and FOLLOW — Share your favorite ROOMS on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Snapchat and more, inviting friends and new followers.

Want more features? Get DIDO now!

Play games while chatting
You can play games like UNO while chatting in Room. Game is on DIDO. You can play games with people all over the world anytime.

Group voice chat
Create voice chat room, invite friends or wait for strangers to join in the chat room, use text or voice to chat with friends, enjoy the fun of a great voice chat party.

Voice chat tag
You can add topic tags to your voice chat rooms. There are different chat tags for chatting, entertainment, singing, and tons more. You can choose the chat room which you are interested in according to the topic. The tag will help you find friends with the same interests more accurately so that you guys will have more topics to talk about.

Awesome virtual gifts
DIDO offers lots of amazing virtual gifts, strengthen the friendship between you and your friends by sending cute virtual gifts. Everyone likes receiving gifts from others. Every gift from a friend is a wish for your happiness.

Easy to register
Use a message and Facebook to sign up for a DIDO account. It is easier and saves you more time. Enjoy your voice chat experience quickly and easily."
descriptionShort: Voice Chat makes laughs happiness surprises new friends

creator: SHFC Technology Limited
descriptionHtml:
DiDO is a voice interaction application that focuses on social interaction among acquaintances, creating an exclusive online gathering space for you
1. Voice tea party, invite three or five friends to start an exclusive voice tea party, share music, read stories or talk about interesting things in life in a comfortable space, just like sitting around a round table in a cafe.
2. Close friends' exclusive chat room, create a personalized theme room, set an exclusive password, and enjoy 24-hour voice companionship with relatives and friends. Each room is like an online living room created by you, and you can start a relaxed conversation in afternoon tea mode at any time.
3. Friends' game night, specially designed 2-6 people collaborative games, with a built-in convenient friend invitation system. You can bring an immersive interactive experience through real-time voice at any time, just like friends sitting around on the carpet in the living room to play games naturally.
Application scenario examples: bedtime story meeting for long-distance girlfriends, online reading club for old classmates - daily voice tea time for family groups, exclusive voice command room for game teams
